WEBVTT

00:01.105 --> 00:02.389
CATHERINE:
<i>Nine years ago,</i>

00:02.555 --> 00:04.971
I witnessed my mother's murder.

00:05.010 --> 00:08.279
I would have been killed, too,
<i>if it hadn't been for Vincent.</i>

00:09.464 --> 00:11.215
You're him.

00:11.217 --> 00:12.883
<i>The things you've done...</i>

00:12.885 --> 00:15.403
VINCENT:
<i>I hate myself for them.</i>

00:15.405 --> 00:19.156
I'm trying to decide
if I belong in a cage.

00:19.158 --> 00:23.160
I just found...
six cases of you

00:23.162 --> 00:25.396
trying to save victims
around the city.

00:25.398 --> 00:27.564
<i>You're not a monster.</i>

00:27.566 --> 00:30.734
<i>You know, that first night</i>
<i>we met in the woods,</i>

00:30.736 --> 00:32.253
<i>I knew...</i>

00:32.255 --> 00:34.905
that you would never hurt me.

00:34.907 --> 00:36.674
Vincent, I want
to have you over for dinner.

00:36.676 --> 00:39.176
<i>And unless there's something</i>
<i>else holding you back,</i>

00:39.178 --> 00:41.078
<i>I hope to see you there.</i>

00:49.237 --> 00:52.056
♪

01:00.282 --> 01:03.117
(steady heartbeat)

01:03.119 --> 01:05.936
(distorted, echoing):
Vincent?

01:05.938 --> 01:07.905
What are you doing?

01:07.907 --> 01:10.040
(object clatters to ground)
Uh...

01:10.042 --> 01:11.742
I'm sorry, I didn't
mean to startle you.

01:11.744 --> 01:13.244
Uh, it's okay, I...

01:13.246 --> 01:18.532
forgot to turn the
security system on again.

01:18.534 --> 01:21.051
What's going on?
Nothing. I... (clears throat)

01:21.053 --> 01:23.454
I just wanted to make
sure that, um...

01:23.456 --> 01:25.789
Is everything okay?

01:25.791 --> 01:29.143
Uh, yeah, I just...
wasn't feeling so great.

01:29.145 --> 01:33.964
So is... that why you didn't
show up for dinner last night?

01:33.966 --> 01:35.983
Uh, yeah.

01:35.985 --> 01:40.187
Because I kind of thought
that you stood me up.

01:40.189 --> 01:44.859
No, I just, uh, should've told
you that I wasn't gonna make it.

01:46.862 --> 01:50.647
Okay, look, I, um...

01:50.649 --> 01:53.284
I found the present you
left me on the windowsill,

01:53.286 --> 01:54.585
which...

01:54.587 --> 01:57.037
was so sweet.

01:57.039 --> 01:59.039
Thank you.
And I realized

01:59.041 --> 02:01.926
that you must have left it
during my birthday party,

02:01.928 --> 02:05.029
which involved many margaritas,

02:05.031 --> 02:06.847
and, uh,
I wondered if, maybe,

02:06.849 --> 02:09.383
when you left it,
you saw me and...

02:09.384 --> 02:11.519
You don't have to give me
an explanation.

02:11.521 --> 02:13.637
So you did see it?

02:13.639 --> 02:17.191
Because... Vincent,
it was just a stupid,

02:17.193 --> 02:19.193
drunken...
You can kiss whoever you want.

02:19.195 --> 02:22.530
No... uh, yeah, I know that.

02:22.532 --> 02:25.165
I mean, it's not like we're...
No.

02:25.167 --> 02:28.619
(laughs)
No, it's not. So...

02:29.654 --> 02:33.073
I'm really sorry
about dinner.

02:33.075 --> 02:35.075
No. It's no big deal.

02:35.077 --> 02:37.912
I just wanted to make sure
that you're okay.

02:37.914 --> 02:40.030
(quietly):
Yeah.

02:40.032 --> 02:41.665
(quietly):
Okay.

02:41.667 --> 02:44.001
Feel better.

02:52.110 --> 02:54.762
♪

02:57.983 --> 03:00.434
♪ In the city

03:00.436 --> 03:02.603
♪ Where I'm from

03:02.605 --> 03:04.521
♪ There are lovers

03:04.523 --> 03:06.240
♪ Till the dawn

03:06.242 --> 03:07.908
♪ And you stayed up

03:07.910 --> 03:10.861
♪ To see the sun

03:10.863 --> 03:14.031
♪ I couldn't wait that long

03:15.033 --> 03:16.533
♪ Gonna get up...

03:16.535 --> 03:19.203
♪

